            "Legacy non-sign-clean source-display policy: source_record_text_display, source_record_label_display, source_record_section_display, source_record_cell_display, and source_record_cell_header_display are source-addressability rows. They may explain a forensic replay/product verdict, but they are not claim-bearing typed derivation.",
